  {"question":"What is a case study method?","options":["Studying many cases superficially","In-depth investigation of a specific instance or organisation","Comparing two countries","Statistical analysis only"],"correct":1,"explanation":"The case study method involves in-depth investigation of a specific instance, organisation, or event."},
